## figures

So many options for figures. 

One is to set figure width/height


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="|7,8"}
---
title: "World Changing Research"
format: html
execute:
  eval: true
  echo: false
fig-width: 6.5
fig-height: 8
---
```
:::


