# Chunk Options

## Chunk Options

Chunk options are typically included in special comments at the top of code chunks

`#|` (think hash pipe?)

This is how you override the global options within a particular chunk


::: {.cell}

````{.cell-code}
```{{r}}
#| eval: false

# comment
a <- 22
a / 7
```
````
:::


